mg class="aligncenter wp-image-975307" src="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1-300x84.png" alt="WPML Compatible themes" width="400" height="112" srcset="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1-300x84.png 300w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1-150x42.png 150w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1.png 568w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" /></p>\n<p>Today we are happy to announce several compatible WPML themes.</p>\n<p>The themes are, <a href="https://themeforest.net/item/upside-multi-purpose-wordpress-theme/14033192" target="_blank">Upside</a>, <a href="https://themeforest.net/item/movement-personal-blog-wordpress-theme/14102366" target="_blank">Movement</a>, <a href="https://lazycatthemes.com/fika/" target="_blank">Fika</a>, <a href="https://themeforest.net/item/liberty-your-political-wordpress-theme/15341403" target="_blank">Liberty</a>, <a href="https://www.lyrathemes.com/kale-pro/" target="_blank">Kale</a>, <a href="https://themeforest.net/item/zoner-real-estate-wordpress-theme/9099226" target="_blank">Zoner</a></p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you‚Äôre a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our¬†<a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Upside</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Upside is the ultimate responsive multi-purpose WordPress theme designed for any kind of business websites, from small to medium-sized enterprises.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/upside-multi-purpose-wordpress-theme/14033192" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Upside</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Movement</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Movement is a personal blog WordPress responsive theme with masonry grid created using HTML5 &#038; SCSS, mobile optimized &#038; retina ready.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/movement-personal-blog-wordpress-theme/14102366" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Movement</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Fika</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Fika is a feature-rich and versatile theme optimized for WordPress food blogs</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://lazycatthemes.com/fika/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Fika</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Liberty</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Theme is dedicated to political parties and candidates.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/liberty-your-political-wordpress-theme/15341403" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Liberty</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Kale</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Kal