tps://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Aadi</h2>\n<blockquote><p>AADI is a comprehensive wordpress theme designed catering to the needs of Architecture, Engineering and other construction related services.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/aadi-construction-wordpress-theme/17271521" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Aadi</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">PE Hotel</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Powerful hotel WordPress theme offers you the ready solution for any hotel,motel, guest house or any other hotel industry sites.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/hotel-old-town-wordpress-theme/17269049" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase PE Hotel</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Esquare</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Esquare is responsive, customisable WordPress theme suitable for Blog, Portfolio or Ecommerce site.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/esquare-responsive-wordpress-blog-theme/13895642" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Esquare</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Bellevue</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Perfect for your vacation rental or hotel. Includes a full booking system, availability calendar and payments through WooCommerce.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/bellevue-hotel-bed-breakfast-booking-theme/12482898" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Bellevue</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">GDayNews</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Blog and Magazine WordPress theme</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.jawtemplates.com/jaw-portfolio/gdn-magazine-blog-video-theme/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase GDayNews</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Kaleidoscope</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Kaleidoscope is a beautiful and easy-to-use, grid-style theme optimized for WordPress food blogs.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://lazycatthemes.com/kaleidoscope/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Kaleidoscope</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Hello Friday</h2>\n<blockquote><p>A beautiful, lifestyle blog theme for creatives, travellers, photographers, foodies, professionals or story tellers.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/hello-friday-elegant-lifestyle-blog-theme/17695139" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Hello Friday</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Focuson</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Fully Responsive and Retina-Ready clean and flexible WordPress Theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/focuson-business-wordpress-theme/15611214" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Focuson</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Labomba</h2>\n<blockquote><p>LABOMBA is a WooComerce based template for your fashion website.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/labomba-responsive-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/6106367" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Labo