ilingual/" target="_blank">works very well, and for a very long time now, with WooCommerce</a>, but sometimes WooCommerce might not be the perfect choice for you, that&#8217;s why we have recently re taken our compatibility project with <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-digital-downloads/" target="_blank">Easy Digital Downloads (EDD)</a>, and updated <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/edd-multilingual/" target="_blank">Easy Digital Downloads  Multilingual plugin</a>.</p>\n<p>EDD might come helpful when you are not selling a physical product, or when you are building a marketplace site.  </p>\n<p>Want to know more? &#8211; read our <a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/related-projects/easy-digital-downloads-multilingual/">full tutorial for going multilingual with Easy Digital Downloads</a>.</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=s-yo8IuMahQ:0aX3XMo-SHo:D7DqB2pKExk"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=s-yo8IuMahQ:0aX3XMo-SHo:D7DqB2pKExk" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=s-yo8IuMahQ:0aX3XMo-SHo:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=s-yo8IuMahQ:0aX3XMo-SHo:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=s-yo8IuMahQ:0aX3XMo-SHo:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=s-yo8IuMahQ:0aX3XMo-SHo:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/s-yo8IuMahQ" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:69:"https://wpml.org/2016/10/easy-digital-downloads-compatible-wpml/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs"